title: French ex-president held over Gaddafi funding
text:
French ex-president held over Gaddafi funding 2:46pm GMT - 01:46 
France's former president Nicolas Sarkozy has been questioned by authorities over a campaign finance probe that could tie him to the late Libyan leader Muammar Gaddafi. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
